# System Tests Directory

This directory will contain end-to-end system tests for the Claude WM CLI.

## Structure

- `config_workflow_test.go` - Complete configuration workflow tests
- `sandbox_development_test.go` - Sandbox development and upstreaming tests
- `migration_scenarios_test.go` - Legacy migration testing
- `integration_scenarios_test.go` - Cross-component integration scenarios

## Test Characteristics

- **Duration**: Up to 10 minutes per test suite
- **Scope**: Full user workflows and realistic scenarios
- **Environment**: Isolated temporary directories
- **Dependencies**: Real file system operations, no mocks

## Running System Tests

```bash
# Run all system tests
make test-system

# Run specific test file
go test ./test/system/ -run TestConfigWorkflow -v

# Run with timeout
go test ./test/system/ -timeout 10m -v
```

## Test Data

System tests use realistic test data and scenarios:

- Fresh project initialization
- Existing project migration
- Complex configuration updates
- Multi-step development workflows
- Error recovery scenarios